            <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">A report fit to print.</p>
            <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">We created a print option driven by the same data, so that any updates would appeal to digital users, while providing an equally compelling experience for analog users that still rely on paper.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="inner-block two-third float-right">
            <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/obesity/print-report.jpg" data-sr="enter right, move 200px">
