      <section class="case-block obesity-white">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-right vertical-center mobile-padded-below">
            <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Intuitive and easy to use.</p>
            <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">We created a narrative to present the data in a logical, easily navigable format. We also improved the browsing experience, with a header that keeps up with you, providing filtering options that allow the user to re-order the rankings without losing their place.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="inner-block two-third float-left">
            <img class="case-block-image" src="../images/obesity/tablet.svg" data-sr="enter left, move 200px">
          </div>
        </div>
