      <section class="case-block character-red">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <img class="case-block-image text-below mobile-padded-below" src="../images/obesity/the-numbers.png">
          <p class="case-block-text-heading medium-length align-center" data-sr>It doesn&rsquo;t have to look complex.</p>
          <p class="case-block-text-subtext medium-length align-center" data-sr>Knowing that too many tables can overwhelm users, we replaced a dozen tables with one interactive chart, complete with controls that enable users to view the data from nine different perspectives, each just a quick toggle away.</p>
        </div>
      </section><!-- END case-block -->

      <section class="case-block not-padded obesity-white">
        <div class="inner-block half absolute-left vertical-center left-padded mobile-container">
          <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Better storytelling makes data digestible.</p>
          <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">We made the data-driven story engaging, intuitive, and interactive so the user can continue reading and learning about the magnitude of the obesity issue, particularly within the highlighted demographics.</p>
        </div>

